{# Mount point for a React island. `Foreground.ts` looks for elements with
   the matching `${className}-init` class and hydrates them with the
   `data-props` JSON. The JSON encoder strips `'`/`"`/`<`, so the value
   is safe inside the single-quoted attribute. #}
